## ğŸ¯ Filters

```python
@bot.on("message:photo")
async def photo_handler(ctx):
    await ctx.reply("ğŸ“¸ Rasm qabul qilindi")
```

Custom filter:

```python
@bot.filter(lambda ctx: ctx.chat.type == "private")
async def private_only(ctx):
    await ctx.reply("Private chat")
```

